milestones.description: Hadlee has taken the most five-wicket hauls (3) in ODIs, going past Gary Gilmour's record
Hadlee has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 66 wickets, going past Lance Cairns's 64
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (21) for SL, going past Duleep Mendis
